 CORAM : MRS. ROSHAN DALVI, J.

 th April, 2015.

P.C. :
Consent decree has been passed.   The original consent 
decree has been issued to the plaintiff No.5. The plaintiff No.5 has 
applied for a fresh consent decree. Only the duplicate consent decree 
is now available on record. The duplicate consent decree cannot be 
issued to any party. A certified copy of the duplicate consent decree 
shall be issued to plaintiff No.5.

 ( ROSHAN DALVI, J. )
